<script src="js/main.js"></script>
<!-- ...existing code... -->
````

2. **Add a canvas element** inside the Chart tab pane:

````html
<!-- filepath: autobargraphs/src/index.html -->
<!-- ...existing code... -->
<div class="tab-pane fade p-4" id="chart" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="chart-tab">
    <canvas id="barChart" width="400" height="200"></canvas>
</div>
<!-- ...existing code... -->
````

